name: Valentine Heart Collograph Set
description:
Perfect for your Valentine sweetheart or anytime art for your walls!
This is an original set of Collograph prints  by Eve Peach.

Colors range from crimson, to pink and cream to teal and persimmon.
Each print measures 6 X 6"  is signed by the artist and arrives mounted on foam core and in a clear protective sleeve.

(Available for individual sale) $80 ea.

name: Butterfly Tree Print
description:
The digital print measures 8"X10" on a 8.5" X11" sheet, with a white border for framing. 

Specifics:
The digital print is reproduced from an mixed media silkscreen by Eve Peach.

It is printed on Epson, water and fade resistant paper with a sturdy matte finish.

All prints are signed and dated by the artist, and arrive sealed in protective sleeve and a sturdy envelope.
